channel.title: Client run32 or run64 both give error messages
channel.description:
So this may sound stupid but I'm not sure if I have a 64 bit or a 32 bit computer. I'm 90% sure I have a 32 bit so when I run it it says... Could not find the main class: jframe. Program will exit. It's obviously there though.... So when I run64 it says
Code (Java): [Select]The system cannot find the path specified.Press any key to continue . . .Now i'm almost positive the class and classpath are set up right because I can run a server. So if you have any idea on how to fix this please respond, or you can try to help by Teamviewing me. Just send pm or add my MSN Tactical_gmodz@hotmail.com Thanks, Tyler
